trans-unit.source: Represents the security settings for the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer sikkerhetsinnstillingene for den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding> class is designed for interoperation with services that implement WS-* specifications.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding>klassen er utformet for bruken med services som implementerer WS-* spesifikasjonene.</xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding>

trans-unit.source: The transport security for this binding is Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) over HTTP, or HTTPS.
trans-unit.target: Transport sikkerheten for denne bindingen er Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) via HTTP eller HTTPS.
